{
  "video_id": "n8yhaFd_GpM",
  "title": "A scientific approach to the paranormal | Carrie Poppy",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12584.0,
      "end_time": 17113.0,
      "text": "Eight years ago, I was haunted by an evil spirit."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20106.0,
      "end_time": 22306.0,
      "text": "I was 25 at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22330.0,
      "end_time": 26767.0,
      "text": "and I was living in a tiny house behind someone else&#39;s house"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26792.0,
      "end_time": 28870.0,
      "text": "in Los Angeles."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28111.0,
      "end_time": 31763.0,
      "text": "It was this guest house, it had kind of been dilapidated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31787.0,
      "end_time": 34466.0,
      "text": "not taken care of for a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34490.0,
      "end_time": 37941.0,
      "text": "And one night, I was sitting there"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37965.0,
      "end_time": 42467.0,
      "text": "and I got this really spooky feeling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42491.0,
      "end_time": 45509.0,
      "text": "kind of the feeling like you&#39;re being watched."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45533.0,
      "end_time": 48552.0,
      "text": "But no one was there except my two dogs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48576.0,
      "end_time": 50454.0,
      "text": "and they were just chewing their feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51128.0,
      "end_time": 54961.0,
      "text": "And I looked around. No one was there."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54985.0,
      "end_time": 59206.0,
      "text": "And I thought, OK, it&#39;s just my imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59230.0,
      "end_time": 61840.0,
      "text": "But the feeling just kept getting worse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61865.0,
      "end_time": 67157.0,
      "text": "and I started to feel this pressure in my chest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67181.0,
      "end_time": 70273.0,
      "text": "sort of like the feeling when you get bad news."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 70297.0,
      "end_time": 73608.0,
      "text": "But it started to sink lower and lower"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73632.0,
      "end_time": 75250.0,
      "text": "and almost hurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 75870.0,
      "end_time": 79604.0,
      "text": "And over the course of that week, this feeling got worse and worse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79628.0,
      "end_time": 85124.0,
      "text": "and I started to become convinced that something was there"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 85148.0,
      "end_time": 88312.0,
      "text": "in my little guest house, haunting me."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 89843.0,
      "end_time": 92958.0,
      "text": "And I started to hear these sounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 92982.0,
      "end_time": 98920.0,
      "text": "this \"whoosh,\" kind of whisper, like something passing through me."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 100305.0,
      "end_time": 104581.0,
      "text": "I called my best friend, Claire, and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 105398.0,
      "end_time": 108557.0,
      "text": "\"I know this is going to sound crazy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 108581.0,
      "end_time": 110645.0,
      "text": "but, um ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 110669.0,
      "end_time": 115648.0,
      "text": "I think there&#39;s a ghost in my house, and I need to get rid of it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 115672.0,
      "end_time": 120200.0,
      "text": "And she said -- she&#39;s very open-minded -- and she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 120440.0,
      "end_time": 121548.0,
      "text": "\"I don&#39;t think you&#39;re crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 121573.0,
      "end_time": 125446.0,
      "text": "I think you just need to do a cleansing ritual.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 125471.0,
      "end_time": 127252.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 127276.0,
      "end_time": 132701.0,
      "text": "\"So get some sage and burn it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 132725.0,
      "end_time": 135222.0,
      "text": "and tell it to go away.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 135247.0,
      "end_time": 138909.0,
      "text": "So I said, \"OK,\" and I went and I bought sage."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 138933.0,
      "end_time": 142994.0,
      "text": "I had never done this before, so I set the sage on fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 143180.0,
      "end_time": 149718.0,
      "text": "waved it about, and said, \"Go away! This is my house! I live here."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 149742.0,
      "end_time": 151375.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t live here!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 152413.0,
      "end_time": 155694.0,
      "text": "But the feeling stayed. Nothing got better."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 155718.0,
      "end_time": 157914.0,
      "text": "And then I started to think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 157938.0,
      "end_time": 160709.0,
      "text": "OK, well now this thing is probably just laughing at me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 160734.0,
      "end_time": 163162.0,
      "text": "because it hasn&#39;t left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 163186.0,
      "end_time": 166411.0,
      "text": "and I probably just look like this impotent, powerless thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 166435.0,
      "end_time": 168670.0,
      "text": "that couldn&#39;t get it to go away."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 168694.0,
      "end_time": 172619.0,
      "text": "So every day I&#39;d come home"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 172643.0,
      "end_time": 178159.0,
      "text": "and you guys, this feeling got so bad that -- I mean, I&#39;m laughing at it now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 178183.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "but I would sit there in bed and cry every night."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 182860.0,
      "end_time": 188159.0,
      "text": "And the feeling on my chest got worse and worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 188183.0,
      "end_time": 191174.0,
      "text": "It was physically painful."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 191199.0,
      "end_time": 194621.0,
      "text": "And I even went to a psychiatrist"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 194645.0,
      "end_time": 198730.0,
      "text": "and tried to get her to prescribe me medicine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 198970.0,
      "end_time": 202199.0,
      "text": "and she wouldn&#39;t just because I don&#39;t have schizophrenia, OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 202223.0,
      "end_time": 204000.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 205757.0,
      "end_time": 212557.0,
      "text": "So finally I got on the internet, and I Googled \"hauntings.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 212581.0,
      "end_time": 215667.0,
      "text": "And I came upon this forum of ghost hunters."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 215691.0,
      "end_time": 218230.0,
      "text": "But these were a special kind of ghost hunters --"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 218470.0,
      "end_time": 219591.0,
      "text": "they were skeptics."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 219615.0,
      "end_time": 225185.0,
      "text": "They believed that every case of ghosts that they had investigated so far"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 225209.0,
      "end_time": 227384.0,
      "text": "had been explained away by science."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 227408.0,
      "end_time": 231351.0,
      "text": "And I was like, \"OK, smart guys, this is what&#39;s happening to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 231376.0,
      "end_time": 235451.0,
      "text": "and if you have an explanation for me, I would love to hear it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 235475.0,
      "end_time": 238685.0,
      "text": "And one of them said, \"OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 238709.0,
      "end_time": 242795.0,
      "text": "Um, have you heard of carbon monoxide poisoning?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 244697.0,
      "end_time": 249159.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 249183.0,
      "end_time": 252530.0,
      "text": "Like, gas poisoning?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 252554.0,
      "end_time": 255533.0,
      "text": "Carbon monoxide poisoning is when you have a gas leak"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 255557.0,
      "end_time": 257000.0,
      "text": "leaking into your home."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 257240.0,
      "end_time": 262852.0,
      "text": "I looked it up, and the symptoms of carbon monoxide poisoning"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 262876.0,
      "end_time": 266600.0,
      "text": "include a pressure on your chest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 266300.0,
      "end_time": 270428.0,
      "text": "auditory hallucinations -- whoosh --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 270452.0,
      "end_time": 274230.0,
      "text": "and an unexplained feeling of dread."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 275651.0,
      "end_time": 278530.0,
      "text": "So that night, I called the gas company."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 278770.0,
      "end_time": 281882.0,
      "text": "I said, \"I have an emergency. I need you to come out."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 281906.0,
      "end_time": 285176.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t want to get into the story now, but I need you to come out.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 285200.0,
      "end_time": 286393.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 286417.0,
      "end_time": 289203.0,
      "text": "They came out. I said, \"I suspect a gas leak.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 289228.0,
      "end_time": 291744.0,
      "text": "They brought their carbon monoxide detector,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 291768.0,
      "end_time": 293809.0,
      "text": "and the man said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 293834.0,
      "end_time": 297297.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s a really good thing that you called us tonight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 297321.0,
      "end_time": 299734.0,
      "text": "because you could have been dead very soon.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 301487.0,
      "end_time": 306854.0,
      "text": "Thirty-seven percent of Americans believe in haunted houses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 306878.0,
      "end_time": 311467.0,
      "text": "and I wonder how many of them have been in one"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 311492.0,
      "end_time": 314484.0,
      "text": "and how many of them have been in danger."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 316603.0,
      "end_time": 321336.0,
      "text": "So that haunting story has led me to my job."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 321360.0,
      "end_time": 324258.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m an investigator, and I&#39;m an investigator in two senses:"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 324282.0,
      "end_time": 325849.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m an investigative journalist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 325874.0,
      "end_time": 329600.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m also an investigator of the claims of the paranormal"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 329840.0,
      "end_time": 331800.0,
      "text": "and claims of the spiritual."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 331104.0,
      "end_time": 332611.0,
      "text": "And that means a few things."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 332636.0,
      "end_time": 336587.0,
      "text": "Sometimes that means that I&#39;m pretending to need an exorcism"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 336611.0,
      "end_time": 341176.0,
      "text": "so I can get -- yes, that&#39;s right! -- so I can go to an exorcist"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 341200.0,
      "end_time": 344806.0,
      "text": "and see if he&#39;s using gimmicks or psychological tricks"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 344830.0,
      "end_time": 347717.0,
      "text": "to try to convince someone that they&#39;re possessed."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 347742.0,
      "end_time": 351640.0,
      "text": "Sometimes that means I&#39;m going undercover in a fringe group"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 351880.0,
      "end_time": 354461.0,
      "text": "which I report on for a podcast that I co-host."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 354485.0,
      "end_time": 359519.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve done over 70 investigations like this with my co-host, Ross."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 359543.0,
      "end_time": 364539.0,
      "text": "I would love to tell you that nine times out of 10, science wins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 364563.0,
      "end_time": 367580.0,
      "text": "saves the day, it&#39;s all explained."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 367830.0,
      "end_time": 368252.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not true."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 368276.0,
      "end_time": 374492.0,
      "text": "The truth is, 10 times out of 10, science wins, it saves the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 374516.0,
      "end_time": 378284.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 386847.0,
      "end_time": 389527.0,
      "text": "And that doesn&#39;t mean there&#39;s no such thing as a mystery."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 389552.0,
      "end_time": 393478.0,
      "text": "Of course there are mysteries, but a mystery is a mystery."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 393502.0,
      "end_time": 395191.0,
      "text": "It is not a ghost."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 396286.0,
      "end_time": 399907.0,
      "text": "Now, I believe there are two kinds of truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 399931.0,
      "end_time": 404282.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s taken me a while to get to this place, but I think this is right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 404306.0,
      "end_time": 405570.0,
      "text": "so hear me out."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 405594.0,
      "end_time": 408748.0,
      "text": "I think there is outer truth and there&#39;s inner truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 408773.0,
      "end_time": 411988.0,
      "text": "So if you say to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 412120.0,
      "end_time": 414685.0,
      "text": "\"There was a man named Jesus and he once existed,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 414709.0,
      "end_time": 416406.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s outer truth, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 416430.0,
      "end_time": 418780.0,
      "text": "And we can go and look at the historical record."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 418804.0,
      "end_time": 421215.0,
      "text": "We can determine whether that seems to be true."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 421239.0,
      "end_time": 423777.0,
      "text": "And I would argue, it does seem to be true."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 423802.0,
      "end_time": 429473.0,
      "text": "If you say, \"Jesus rose from the dead,\" -- ooh, trickier."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 429497.0,
      "end_time": 431724.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 432261.0,
      "end_time": 439200.0,
      "text": "I would say that&#39;s an outer-truth claim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 439224.0,
      "end_time": 441262.0,
      "text": "because he physically rose or he didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 441286.0,
      "end_time": 444120.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not going to get into whether he rose or he didn&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 444360.0,
      "end_time": 446114.0,
      "text": "but I would say that&#39;s an outer-truth claim."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 446138.0,
      "end_time": 447832.0,
      "text": "It happened or it didn&#39;t happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 447856.0,
      "end_time": 451558.0,
      "text": "But if you say, \"I don&#39;t care whether he rose from the dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 451582.0,
      "end_time": 453926.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s symbolically important to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 453950.0,
      "end_time": 457444.0,
      "text": "and that metaphor is so meaningful, so purposeful to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 457468.0,
      "end_time": 459771.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m not going to try to persuade you of it,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 459795.0,
      "end_time": 462350.0,
      "text": "now you&#39;ve moved it from outer truth to inner truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 462374.0,
      "end_time": 463896.0,
      "text": "from science to art."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 463920.0,
      "end_time": 467840.0,
      "text": "And I think we have a tendency to not be clear about this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 467108.0,
      "end_time": 470520.0,
      "text": "to try to move our inner truths to outer truths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 470544.0,
      "end_time": 473447.0,
      "text": "or to not be fair about it to each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 473471.0,
      "end_time": 475835.0,
      "text": "and when people are telling us their inner truths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 475859.0,
      "end_time": 479469.0,
      "text": "to try to make them defend them by outer-truth standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 479494.0,
      "end_time": 483100.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m talking here about outer truth, about objective things."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 483340.0,
      "end_time": 488719.0,
      "text": "And there was an objective reality in my haunted house, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 488744.0,
      "end_time": 490793.0,
      "text": "Now that I&#39;ve told you about the gas leak,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 490817.0,
      "end_time": 492837.0,
      "text": "I doubt a single person here would be like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 492861.0,
      "end_time": 494835.0,
      "text": "\"I still think there was a ghost, too\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 494859.0,
      "end_time": 495899.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 495923.0,
      "end_time": 498670.0,
      "text": "because as soon as we have these scientific explanations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 498694.0,
      "end_time": 500356.0,
      "text": "we know to give up the ghost."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 500380.0,
      "end_time": 504390.0,
      "text": "We use these things as stopgaps for things that we can&#39;t explain."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 504414.0,
      "end_time": 506414.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t believe them because of evidence;"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 506439.0,
      "end_time": 509201.0,
      "text": "we believe them because of a lack of evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 510202.0,
      "end_time": 512566.0,
      "text": "So there is a group in Los Angeles"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 512590.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516298.00000000006,
      "text": "called the Independent Investigations Group, or the IIG,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 516322.0,
      "end_time": 518302.0,
      "text": "and they do great work."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 518326.0,
      "end_time": 521290.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll give a $10,000 prize"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 521530.0,
      "end_time": 525580.0,
      "text": "to anyone who can show, under scientific conditions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 525604.0,
      "end_time": 527959.0,
      "text": "that they have a paranormal ability."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 527983.0,
      "end_time": 529689.0,
      "text": "No one&#39;s done it yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 529713.0,
      "end_time": 534771.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;ve had a couple people who claim that they were clairaudients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 534795.0,
      "end_time": 538851.0,
      "text": "which means that they can hear voices either from the great beyond"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 538875.0,
      "end_time": 540773.0,
      "text": "or they can read minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 540797.0,
      "end_time": 543557.0,
      "text": "And they had one person who was very sincere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 543581.0,
      "end_time": 546472.0,
      "text": "who believed that he could read minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 546565.0,
      "end_time": 552552.0,
      "text": "So they set up a test with him, and this is the way it always works."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 552576.0,
      "end_time": 554822.0,
      "text": "The group says, \"OK, we have a protocol,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 554846.0,
      "end_time": 556861.0,
      "text": "we have a way to scientifically test this."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 556885.0,
      "end_time": 558380.0,
      "text": "Do you agree with it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 558620.0,
      "end_time": 559958.0,
      "text": "The person says yes. Then they test it."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 559982.0,
      "end_time": 561987.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very important that both sides agree."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 562110.0,
      "end_time": 564425.0,
      "text": "They did that, they tested him."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 564450.0,
      "end_time": 567400.0,
      "text": "They said, \"OK, you know what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 567280.0,
      "end_time": 570870.0,
      "text": "You weren&#39;t able to predict what Lisa was thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 570894.0,
      "end_time": 572923.0,
      "text": "It matched up about the same as chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 572947.0,
      "end_time": 574789.0,
      "text": "Looks like you don&#39;t have the power.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 574813.0,
      "end_time": 576663.0,
      "text": "And that gave them the opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 576687.0,
      "end_time": 581956.0,
      "text": "to compassionately sit down with him and have a very difficult discussion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 581980.0,
      "end_time": 583949.0,
      "text": "which basically amounted to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 583973.0,
      "end_time": 588536.0,
      "text": "\"Hey, we know you&#39;re sincere, and what that means is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 588560.0,
      "end_time": 590839.0,
      "text": "you do hear something in your head.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 590917.0,
      "end_time": 595525.0,
      "text": "And that guy got to make the very difficult decision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 595583.0,
      "end_time": 601661.0,
      "text": "but really the life-changing decision about whether to go get help."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 601728.0,
      "end_time": 606771.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re actually helping people to make these connections"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 606795.0,
      "end_time": 612104.0,
      "text": "that maybe before seemed like otherworldly explanations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 612129.0,
      "end_time": 617189.0,
      "text": "help draw us into reality and maybe change our lives for the better."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 618293.0,
      "end_time": 624850.0,
      "text": "Now, on the other hand, maybe one time it&#39;ll turn out to be true."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 624708.0,
      "end_time": 626731.0,
      "text": "Maybe we&#39;ll find out there are ghosts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 626755.0,
      "end_time": 628928.0,
      "text": "and holy shit, it will be the best thing!"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 628952.0,
      "end_time": 631676.0,
      "text": "And every time I do one of these investigations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 631700.0,
      "end_time": 633506.0,
      "text": "I still get so excited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 633530.0,
      "end_time": 635593.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m like 75 into them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 635617.0,
      "end_time": 639694.0,
      "text": "and still I swear on number 76, I&#39;m going to be like, \"This is the one!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 639718.0,
      "end_time": 640923.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 640947.0,
      "end_time": 645803.0,
      "text": "Maybe I&#39;m just eternally optimistic, but I hope I never lose this hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 645827.0,
      "end_time": 649602.0,
      "text": "and I invite you to take this same attitude"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 649626.0,
      "end_time": 652690.0,
      "text": "when people share their outer beliefs with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 652930.0,
      "end_time": 654560.0,
      "text": "When talking about testable claims,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 654584.0,
      "end_time": 658262.0,
      "text": "respect them enough to ask these good questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 658287.0,
      "end_time": 661149.0,
      "text": "Challenge and see how you can examine them together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 661173.0,
      "end_time": 665342.0,
      "text": "because there&#39;s this idea that you can&#39;t respect a belief"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 665366.0,
      "end_time": 667915.0,
      "text": "and still challenge it, but that&#39;s not true."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 667940.0,
      "end_time": 670687.0,
      "text": "When we jiggle the lock, when we test the claim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 670711.0,
      "end_time": 674683.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re saying, OK, I respect you, I&#39;m listening to what you&#39;re saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 674707.0,
      "end_time": 676699.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to test it out with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 676723.0,
      "end_time": 680780.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve all had that experience where you&#39;re telling someone something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 680102.0,
      "end_time": 682833.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re like, \"Oh, that&#39;s really interesting, yeah,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 682857.0,
      "end_time": 684980.0,
      "text": "you know you&#39;re being had."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 685400.0,
      "end_time": 688294.0,
      "text": "But when someone says, \"Really? Huh."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 689413.0,
      "end_time": 691803.0,
      "text": "Sounds a little sketchy to me, but I&#39;m listening,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 691827.0,
      "end_time": 694484.0,
      "text": "you at least know you&#39;re being engaged and respected."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 694508.0,
      "end_time": 697624.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the kind of attitude we should have with these claims."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 697648.0,
      "end_time": 700355.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s showing someone that you care what they&#39;re saying."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 700379.0,
      "end_time": 703315.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s respect."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 706300.0,
      "end_time": 710728.0,
      "text": "Now, yes, most of these searches will come up empty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 710753.0,
      "end_time": 712586.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s how all of science works."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 712983.0,
      "end_time": 717840.0,
      "text": "Every cure for cancer so far has not panned out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 717108.0,
      "end_time": 719439.0,
      "text": "but we don&#39;t stop looking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 719464.0,
      "end_time": 720994.0,
      "text": "for two reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 721180.0,
      "end_time": 723496.0,
      "text": "Because number one, the answer matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 723520.0,
      "end_time": 727542.0,
      "text": "Whether it&#39;s looking at the afterlife or the paranormal or the cure for cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 727566.0,
      "end_time": 729899.0,
      "text": "it all amounts to the same question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 729923.0,
      "end_time": 732602.0,
      "text": "How long will we be here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 733785.0,
      "end_time": 737569.0,
      "text": "And two, because looking for the truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 737593.0,
      "end_time": 738901.0,
      "text": "being open-minded,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 738926.0,
      "end_time": 743295.0,
      "text": "and being willing to be wrong and to change your whole worldview"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 743319.0,
      "end_time": 745367.0,
      "text": "is awe-inspiring."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 746138.0,
      "end_time": 749951.0,
      "text": "I still get excited at ghost stories every single time."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 749975.0,
      "end_time": 753590.0,
      "text": "I still consider that every group I join might be right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 753830.0,
      "end_time": 755790.0,
      "text": "and I hope I never lose that hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 755104.0,
      "end_time": 756908.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s all never lose that hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 756932.0,
      "end_time": 759787.0,
      "text": "because searching for what&#39;s out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 759811.0,
      "end_time": 761725.0,
      "text": "helps us understand what&#39;s in here."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 762457.0,
      "end_time": 768918.0,
      "text": "And also, please have a carbon monoxide detector in your home."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 769982.0,
      "end_time": 771261.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 771285.0,
      "end_time": 776249.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}